flowchart TD

        MP[Logistics_StockLevel]
    end

    R --> MS
    F --> MF

    subgraph Refresh[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        C[Logistics_Warehouse] -->|reuse| RU[Logistics_DeliveryRoute]
        C -->|clean| NI[Logistics_StockLevel]
    end

    T --> C
    RU --> MR
    PS[Logistics_Warehouse] --> MP

    classDef metric fill:#eef,stroke:#336
    class MS,MF,MR,MP metric
